mkv2cast (1.2.8-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Add GPG signing support for APT repository
  * Add GPG key generation and export scripts
  * Add comprehensive package signing documentation
  * Update installation instructions with GPG verification
  * Enhance security with improved .gitignore for key protection
  * Support both passphrase-protected and unprotected GPG keys

