mkv2cast (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release
  * Intelligent codec detection (H.264, H.265/HEVC, AV1)
  * Hardware acceleration (VAAPI, Intel QSV)
  * Parallel processing with pipeline mode
  * Rich progress UI with multiple workers
  * Automatic French audio track selection
  * Integrity checking
  * XDG Base Directory compliance
  * Conversion history with SQLite

